data.description: YOUR SEARCH HAS ENDED!  WELCOME HOME to this lovely 3 bdrm/2 full bath RANCH situated on a BASEMENT WITH DAYLIGHT WINDOWS awaiting your finishes to provide lots of extra living space! You will be greeted by a sprawling living room upon entry with a ceiling fan and nice natural light from the plentiful windows!  The kitchen is well equipped with nice cabinetry, a window sink, and all kitchen appliances remain with the home! The laundry room is a nice size with shelving and is conveniently located on the first level! Enjoy the tranquility of being nestled toward the end of a cul-de-sac! This home features a 2 car garage, side deck and more! Stacy Springs is conveniently located close to the east end bridge and just minutes from Louisville, shopping, dining, and the arts! Staying close on this side of the river to enjoy all that the heart of Jeffersonville now offers will be enjoyable as well!  KEYS AT CLOSING!  Call, email or text today to tour this lovely home! Rm Sz & Sq Ft Approx.
